mengira aku adalah Tuan Rama?'

00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:41.360
'Oh ya!'

00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:43.000
'Biarkan aku menikmati ini.'

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:44.840
Anak saya.

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:46.320
Duduk.

